Class Fonts

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team23.weather.gui.Fonts

  • public class Fonts
extends java.lang.Object
    The Fonts are a collection of predefined Font Styles and sizes. The Fonts come in Small, Medium, and Large. The Font Style is Dialog.
    Author:
    Saquib Mian
